 to be eco-friendly |last=Lai |first=Tim |date=September 11, 2007 |work=[[Toronto Star]] |access-date=September 12, 2007 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ee1M8C8G?url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2007/09/11/citys_film_industry_aim_to_be_ecofriendly.html |archive-date=February 23, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LouCameo\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2429308/lou-ferrigno-says-hulk-cameo-a-smash/ |title=Lou Ferrigno Says Hulk Cameo A 'Smash' |last=Adler |first=Shawn |date=October 23, 2007 |access-date=October 27, 2007 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EdUs0ZtZ?url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/23/lou-ferrigno-says-hulk-cameo-a-smash/ |archive-date=February 23, 2013 |publisher=[[MTV]] Movies Blog}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ElliottMTV\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2429358/hulk-stars-give-thumbs-up-for-sequel-counterparts-marvel-goes-red/ |title='Hulk' Stars Give Thumbs-Up For Sequel Counterparts; Marvel Goes Red |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |date=November 2, 2007 |access-date=November 3, 2007 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EdVH8LRp?url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/11/02/hulk-stars-give-thumbs-up-for-sequel-counterparts-marvel-goes-red/ |archive-date=February 23, 2013 |publisher=[[MTV]] Movies Blog}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TylerUSAToday\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-11-29-liv-tyler_N.htm |title=Liv Tyler loves being the Givenchy girl |last=Freydkin |first=Donna |date=November 29, 2007 |work=[[USA Today]] |access-date=December 10, 2007 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Edg02fFG?url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-11-29-liv-tyler_N.htm |archive-date=February 23, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"HurtMTV\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1579965/william-hurt-says-new-hulk-is-more-heroic-reveals-iron-man-crossover-scene/ |title=William Hurt Says New Hulk Is More Heroic, Reveals Iron Man Cross