an |date=April 18, 2012 |publisher=[[Newsarama]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6kIcfGF2F?url=http://www.newsarama.com/9410-incredible-hulk-annotations-green-goliath-to-marvel-movies.html |archive-date=September 5, 2016 |access-date=September 5, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Phase1Timeline\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/1652489/why-marvel-movies-dont-overlap-like-they-used-to-according-to-kevin-feige |title=Why Marvel Movies Don\u2019t Overlap Like They Used To, According To Kevin Feige |last=Eisenberg |first=Eric |date=April 27, 2017 |publisher=CinemaBlend |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6q49CQQNK?url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1652489/why-marvel-movies-dont-overlap-like-they-used-to-according-to-kevin-feige |archive-date=April 28, 2017 |access-date=April 28, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IM2Timeline\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/2010/05/10-things-parents-should-know-about-iron-man-2/ |title=10 Things Parents Should Know About Iron Man 2 |last=Cornelius |first=Doug |date=May 8, 2010 |website=[[Wired (magazine)|Wired]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6rvnQIX3d?url=https://www.wired.com/2010/05/10-things-parents-should-know-about-iron-man-2/ |archive-date=July 13, 2017 |access-date=July 13, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RuffaloUSAToday\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/10/30/mark-ruffalo-hulk-avengers-thor/74878150/ |title=Mark Ruffalo: A solo Hulk movie 'feels even further away' than before |last=Ryan |first=Patrick |date=October 30, 2015 |website=USA Today |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6dIfbBesg?url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/entertainthis/2015/10/30/mark-ruffalo-hulk-avengers-thor/74878150/ |archive-date=November 25, 2015 |access-date=November 25, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RuffaloJuly2017\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/hulk-mark-ruffalo-avengers-infinity-war-di